                     <interp inst="def2-307-18730407" type="given" value="DAVID"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">DAVID ABRAMS</hi> (22)</persName>
                  <rs id="t18730407-307-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18730407-307-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18730407-307-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>, Stealing two purses and 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the property of a person unknown.</rs>
